author: kylem
msg: Added support for persisting listener relationships, and persistence delegate classes for generated adaptors.   There is now a checkin test that encodes to XML, then decodes from XML a control containing two nested controls, some non-default state, and several listener relationships.   After decode, some basic tests are made to see if state/relationships have been preserved.

author: rgoers
msg: fix for bug 33091. JSR-168 Portlet urls do not contain event id's (if configured).

author: dolander
msg: Add a test demonstrating the "sticky" nature of tree creation when the
tree is created by JSP tags.  This is in response to Jira bug 166.
